headline: Match Group downgraded by JP Morgan amid Tinder challenges
summary: Investing.com -- JP Morgan downgraded the Match Group Inc (NASDAQ:MTCH) to "neutral" from "overweight" and cut its price target to $33 from $40, given ongoing struggles with Tinder’s turnaround.
